<snippet>
	<content><![CDATA[const redirect = (url, asLink = true) =>
  asLink ? (window.location.href = url) : window.location.replace(url);]]></content>
	<description>Redirects to a specified URL.  Use `window.location.href` or `window.location.replace()` to redirect to `url`. Pass a second argument to simulate a link click (`true` - default) or an HTTP redirect (`false`).</description>
